A taxi boss was sprayed with bullets outside Msunduzi Taxi Rank in KwaXimba, outside Cato Ridge on Wednesday morning. A total of 28 cartridges were found scattered all over the scene. It is alleged that while the taxi boss was inside his vehicle, which was parked outside the rank, a group of men in a silver grey Etios came and opened fire at him. The gunmen then fled the scene.Â Police are at the scene with more than 200 community members surrounding the scene in shock. *This is a developing story.